<s> There do not appear to be any rules saying that line endings in XQuery text are normalized.  </s>
<s> This means that the query: gotcha!  </s>
<s> will return a different infoset depending on how the text editor used to prepare the query represents line endings, and it will potentially produce a different infoset from the one produced by an XML parser when applied to the same input.  </s>
<s> I would recommend that line endings within XQuery input text should be normalized in the same way as XML line endings.  </s>
<s> And to avoid having to change the rules in the future, I would suggest that we use the XML 1.1 rules rather than the XML 1.0 rules.  </s>
<s> This rule should not apply to XPath; preprocessing of XPath input is the job of the host language.  </s>
<s> Michael Kay Software AG  </s>
<s> How do they differ between XML 1.0 and 1.1?  </s>
